Long afterward Amory thought of sophomore spring as the happiest time of his life . 
His ideas were in tune with life as he found it he wanted no more than to drift and dream and enjoy a dozen new found friendships through the April afternoons . 
Alec Connage came into his room one morning and woke him up into the sunshine and peculiar glory of Campbell Hall shining in the window . 
