CRESCENDO ! Next day , by a merciful chance , passed in a whirl . 
Isabelle and her mother drove into town at four , and they rode up smiling Prospect Avenue , through the gay crowd , to have tea at Cottage . 
She was all he had expected , and he was happy and eager to make that night the centre of every dream . 
The next day was another whirl . 
The stag line is a most homogeneous mass of men . 
It fairly sways with a single soul . 
