Oh , mother CECELIA Mothers gone down . 
One's a hoop skirt with pantaloons the other's a one piece bathing suit . 
I'm quite charming in both of them . 
You're glad so you can get married and live on Long Island with the fast younger married set . 
You want life to be a chain of flirtation with a man for every link . 
ROSALIND Want it to be one ! You mean I've found it one . 
